			subtitle: "Copper + Zinc + heat = the future."
			description: [
				"Brass is the material that unlocks everything interesting in Create."
				"Mix Copper and Zinc Ingots in a Mechanical Mixer running at 130+ RPM."
				"If your wheel doesn't spin fast enough, build a bigger one. Or two. Size matters here."
