			title: "Mechanical Crafter"
			icon: "create:mechanical_crafter"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 4.0d
			subtitle: "Crafting, but make it automated."
			description: [
				"The Mechanical Crafter automates crafting recipes that are too complex — or impossible — for a regular table."
				"Several key items in this modpack, including the Resource Catalyst, can ONLY be made here."
				"You need at least 3 Crafters arranged in a crafting grid pattern. Items enter from the back and get crafted automatically."
				"Build a 3x3 grid of Crafters for full recipe coverage."
