			title: "Precision Mechanism"
			icon: "create:precision_mechanism"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 6.0d
			subtitle: "The most important item in Tier 2."
			description: [
				"The Precision Mechanism is the gatekeeper of Tier 3."
				"It requires a 5x5 Mechanical Crafter setup — and quite a few intermediate components."
				"Recipe involves: Gold Nuggets, Electron Tubes, Shaft, Iron Nuggets, and a Cogwheel."
				"Without this item you cannot build the AE2 ME Controller. There is no shortcut."
				"Build the crafter setup carefully. Run the recipe. Enjoy the satisfying animation."
