			title: "Mechanical Arm"
			icon: "create:mechanical_arm"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 8.0d
			subtitle: "It grabs things. That's literally it. It rules."
			description: [
				"The Mechanical Arm picks up items from one machine and deposits them into another."
				"It replaces dozens of funnels, belts, and workarounds with a single configurable block."
				"Set its inputs (e.g., Crushing Wheels output) and outputs (e.g., Enrichment Chamber input) using a Wrench."
				"Build one for your ore chain: Crushing Wheels → Arm → Mekanism Enricher. Watch the magic happen."
			]
