			description: [
				"Osmium is Mekanism's primary metal — used in almost every machine, circuit, and component."
				"It spawns in large veins deeper than iron, with a higher-than-vanilla density thanks to our ore config."
				"You'll need a lot of it. Start stockpiling now — your future self will thank you."
