			x: 4.0d
			y: 2.0d
			subtitle: "Double ore output. The smart way."
			description: [
				"The Enrichment Chamber processes Crushed Ore (from Create Crushing Wheels) into Dust — giving 2x ore output."
				"This machine requires Forge Energy (FE). Connect it to a Create: New Age Alternator or a solar panel."
				"Important: The recipe for this machine has been modified. You need Create Cogwheels as a crafting component."
				"No Brass-tier Create setup = no Enrichment Chamber. The progression is intentional."
			]
			dependencies: [
