				"This is the full Tier 2 ore chain: mine ore → Crushing Wheels → Enrichment Chamber → smelt dust → ingot."
				"Result: 2 ingots per ore block instead of 1. Every ore block. For the rest of the game."
				"Set up the full automation: belts and arms feeding ore in, ingots coming out automatically."
				"The days of smelting raw ore are over. Never look back."
			]
