			x: 4.0d
			y: 6.0d
			subtitle: "Because regular alloys weren't fancy enough."
			description: [
				"The Metallurgical Infuser combines metals with infuse-type materials (Carbon, Redstone, Diamond, etc.) to create Alloys."
				"Infused Alloy → Reinforced Alloy → Atomic Alloy — each tier unlocks more advanced Mekanism components."
				"To get started: smelt Coal in a furnace to get Carbon Dust (or use the Crusher), then infuse Iron Ingots with Carbon."
				"You'll need Infused Alloy for almost everything in Tier 3 and beyond."
			]
